parameters:
\nc<???>If possible, I'd like you to start working right away, is
that okay?

\nc<Saki>(They did say they would contact me later... but this is too
soon! Is this really okay?)

\nc<???>Same-day interview, same-day hiring. If you're going to
pass, it's better to let you know sooner, right?
\bustMsgExpression[2, 2]\nc<???>So, what do you say? I'd like a quick response.

\bustMsgExpression[2, 0]\nc<???>Good answer. I'm Uchitome Meary, who will be your direct
supervisor. Feel free to call me "Senpai".

\nc<Senpai>We don't have much time, so let's get started right away.
I'll teach you what you need to do.
